org.batfish.symbolic

Class GraphEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.symbolic.GraphEdge

  • public class GraphEdge
extends java.lang.Object
    An edge in the network graph. Contains the router and interface as well as the peer router and interface. Each edge can also be abstract, as in the case of iBGP, or concrete where it corresponds to a particular edge in the topology. There is an invariant that whenever peer == null, it must be that end == null
